        <Parent_String>stainless steel [300010920], chrome steel [300010918], alloy steel [300010917], steel (alloy) [300133751], iron alloy [300010904], iron and iron alloy [300241605], metal by composition or origin [300010901], metal [300010900], inorganic material [300010360], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
